title: The Science of Interstellar with Christopher Nolan
description: Unravel the mysteries of Interstellar when Neil deGrasse Tyson interviews filmmaker and auteur Christopher Nolan. In-studio, Eugene Mirman and cosmologist Dr. Janna Levin help keep the conversation down-to-earth.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
